Description: The package is an attempt to replicate detection of abusive, hateful and normal language on Twitter. 
    The model in this package is a logistic regression model for text classification. 
    It implements multiclass classification for various types of text on Twitter and gives 75% accuracy. 
    Additionally, a word cloud and bar graphs are displayed as part of an exploratory data analysis.
